name: DPC EEU Division I Winter Tour - 2021/2022 presented by Epic Esports Events
description: The International 10 has been a true underdog story, where Team Spirit came out victorious. Now it’s time for a new season to begin, with DPC points up for grabs, the stakes have never been higher. Which team will emerge victorious in the highly competitive Eastern European region? We wil find out soon enough!
